              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-948-ROGP-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-948-ROGP-line-1" n="1">Jason, the valiant prince of Greece,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-948-ROGP-line-2" n="2">From Colchos brought the golden fleece:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-948-ROGP-line-3" n="3">We comb the wool, refine the stuff,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-948-ROGP-line-4" n="4">For modern Jasons that's enough.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-948-ROGP-line-5" n="5">Oh! could we tame yon watchful dragon,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-948-ROGP-line-6" n="6">Old Jason would have less to brag on.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
